.Xr kldnext 2 ,
.Xr kldunload 2 ,
.Xr modfind 2 ,
.Xr modnext 2 ,
.Xr modstat 2 ,
.Xr kld 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Fn kldsym
system call first appeared in
.Fx 3.0 .
